23:15.040 --> 23:15.900
Dinda Yong'er.

23:16.550 --> 23:17.610
Dinda tak apa-apa?

23:18.480 --> 23:19.210
Tak apa-apa.

23:21.600 --> 23:22.150
Ini...

23:25.440 --> 23:26.270
Jangan tengok.

23:26.270 --> 23:27.130
Jangan tengok.

23:27.550 --> 23:28.830
Dinda merayu kepada kanda,

23:28.830 --> 23:29.560
cepat pergi,

23:29.830 --> 23:31.230
